				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/Giang-h%C3%A0nh-th%E1%BB%A9-H%E1%BB%93ng-Ch%C3%A2u-ki%E1%BB%83m-ch%C3%ADnh-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-ZvYD6gjeiEdjQD37kI-XQw">Giang hành thứ Hồng Châu kiểm chính vận - 江行次洪州檢正韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/H%C3%A0n-than-%C4%91%C3%A3i-phi%E1%BA%BFm-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-vu0tjwSQvoDVXz1RmWNmpg">Hàn than đãi phiếm kỳ 2 - 寒灘待泛其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/L%E1%BA%A1p-nh%E1%BA%ADt-du-C%C3%B4-s%C6%A1n-ph%E1%BB%8Fng-Hu%E1%BB%87-C%E1%BA%A7n-Hu%E1%BB%87-T%C6%B0-nh%E1%BB%8B-t%C4%83ng/poem-GGRnUYQ8KyDAE991NSHYSA">Lạp nhật du Cô sơn phỏng Huệ Cần, Huệ Tư nhị tăng - 臘日遊孤山訪惠勤惠思二僧</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%93-Long/L%E1%BB%AF-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-aCBCmu1WKPRgKiXS5Htdig">Lữ hoài kỳ 3 - 旅懷其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%93-Long/author--9TnyXqqJ0jrOvcw26zfjw">Đồ Long</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ly-tao/poem-lRoe60dlSbBq5oc1ZRJWhQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/S%E1%BB%9F-ki%E1%BA%BFn-h%C3%A0nh/poem-7zX_fvrqSHORA8aiuARZQw">Sở kiến hành - 所見行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-S%C6%B0-T%C3%ADch/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%E1%BB%99-Long-giang/poem-8KpnmWX5YaF8l2MUxVYOmw">Thu dạ độ Long giang - 秋夜渡龍江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-S%C6%B0-T%C3%ADch/author-jprWk1DY-7bDKjtVQ3GaZQ">Đào Sư Tích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-t%C3%ACnh-bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-AGKUOTf4MNBoRtTrY2zw2A">Trần tình biểu - 陳情表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/author-2WZpsdSFEWvTQerf8uTifQ">Lý Mật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Qu%C3%A1n-hi%E1%BB%87p-lu%E1%BA%ADt/poem-JAXfd8uaDzucydYeL8fqlg">Trịnh Quán hiệp luật - 鄭瓘協律</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%C3%A2n-Khanh/Xu%C3%A2n-du/poem-oH0DnnWfq5Yohx_3ZEfESA">Xuân du - 春遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%C3%A2n-Khanh/author-JfNmtEKPYaXz7TVdQUy0-Q">Phạm Nhân Khanh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
